archimate:Requirement.name: SY.1.2.3d: d) ensuring that the source of program code, such as HTML, JavaScript and other client-side scripting languages does not contain unnecessary information (e.g. comments and details of functions).
archimate:Requirement.documentation: This is a standard topic modelled from the 2022 Version of the Standards Of Good Practice by ISF. It has been adopted as version 3 of the Security Baseline.
